{"tid":1250895,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"621 散場後，無配帶委任證人士管有違禁武器，意圖攻勢市民","createTime":"2019-06-22T09:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T13:17:04.000Z","uid":37232,"like":70,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"02d81e7cfed46e6cef3dba81f8fde570f3218d99","tid":1250895,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:12:07.000Z","msg":"片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CdW3U53fq9M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCdW3U53fq9M&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2Bh1wLDRbgpiba54y0vEBNjMo%3D&h=58a91de3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CdW3U53fq9M</a><br />\n<br />\n第217章 《武器條例》第4條<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;違禁武器&rdquo; (prohibited weapon)指附表內指明的任何武器</span>；<br />\n違禁武器<br />\n中國式飛鏢<br />\n重力刀<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">重力操作鋼棒</span><br />\n指節套，不論是否有尖釘及是否有刀刃<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;管有&rdquo; (possession)，就違禁武器或武術兵器而言，包括任何人或武術團體對由任何其他人或團體所保管武器的控制。<br />\n<br />\n3.適用範圍<br />\n第II部<span style=\"color: red;\">不適用於</span> &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(b)<span style=\"color: red;\">任何人代表香港政府管有違禁武器</span>或武術兵器....<br />\n....<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(iii)香港警務處</span><br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n4.管有違禁武器<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">任何人管有違禁武器，即屬犯罪，可處罰款$10,000及監禁3年。</span><br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap217!zh-Hant-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap217%21zh-Hant-HK&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2Bh1wLDRbgpiba54y0vEBNjMo%3D&h=7b14d09a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap217!zh-Hant-HK</a>"},{"pid":"34c622e1663687186fd0cf42898202d252e7d752","tid":1250895,"uid":34877,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:15:26.000Z","msg":"咩委任證？明明係暴徒 黑社會 警察點做野"},{"pid":"58ee7f29f9147e6301d6e2e31f51fe0600e7de3b","tid":1250895,"uid":184096,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,